
UHLabelView
by Umer Hanif Sheikh
============================================================================

An advanced Label View for multi-style text rendering with multi-column 
support.

UHLabelView.m - Primary View for Rendering the NSAttributedString

MainViewController.m - Example of using the UHLabelView

The real motivation of posting this project on GitHub is to implement 
selection and Magnifer Loupe in the Label View from Community input.

Thanks, Please contribute to the project.

Please feel to email me at umer@umerh.com

Known Issues:
* Background Color is only white



